Confirmed:  These are from SEASON 3.   There is no season 4 yet (As of this posting, S03E62 & S03E63 were just uploaded yesterday after airing this week).  It's a convenient way to get 28 episodes from season 3 in one torrent, but that's it.

To further specify:  The link to wiki in the description lists episodes as being part of season 4 which are on TPB as "S03EXX".  On the wiki link, the episode numbers on Season 3 only go up to 26, whereas here, season 3 is up to 63 episodes.  If you download all of the "S03EXX" episodes, then you already have every episode in this torrent.
